			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": " - Go to camp to Trigger first camp night\r\n- come back to level\r\n- use code: oe qnight NIGHT_MonitorIntro_a9297517-ab4d-482d-b287-fc6e7001d93e\r\n- move a distance and have supplies to trigger second camp night\r\n- Don't have Laezel in party or will trigger different cinematic\r\n- After talking with monitor in camp he will teleport you to Dinner hall for this cinematic to start"
				},
